      <para id="id1170748778884">Use the given 16 point star to mind map your interests and your personality traits (the type of person you are).</para>
      <para id="id1170752111340">Using these ideas, design an A4 sized <emphasis effect="bold">mini-poster</emphasis> for your bedroom door, illustrating these special interests and who you are.</para>
      <para id="id1170749273157">Only use words, pictures and coloured strips of paper, <emphasis effect="bold">torn from magazines</emphasis> and pasted down. Try to fill every conceivable opening or space.</para>
      <para id="id8886751">Laminate your project before displaying it in class and at home.</para>
