      <para id="id1170746695278">In your groups, do the following –</para>
      <para id="id1170746565106"> Brainstorm the problems teenagers experience today.</para>
      <para id="id1170751829663"> Still in groups, list these problems in order of importance or severity.</para>
      <para id="id1170748308811"> How can these problems be avoided?</para>
      <para id="id1170748560121"> What is the best way of handling any such problem?</para>
      <para id="id1170748473482"> Would you allow someone to help you with a particular problem?</para>
      <para id="id5573207"> Report to your peers. How do your ideas compare to theirs?</para>
