      <para id="id1170747316726"><emphasis effect="bold">Read</emphasis> the letters printed below. Select one, <emphasis effect="bold">think carefully</emphasis> about the contents and answer it as if you are Sister Mildred, Dr Dee or Dr Phil, giving the writer <emphasis effect="bold">good and sound advice.</emphasis></para>
